<p>Our BU chapter has some specific goals in mind:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Incorporate new/prospective CS students into the BU CS community</li>
  <li>Provide workshops and resources to CS students that will introduce them to sub-fields of computer science</li>
  <li>Demonstrate how other fields/majors can be incorporated with computer science to create new and exciting projects (cross-denominational work)</li>
</ul>
